About Us
Dock, Dine & Unwind
The Chubby Mullet Bar & Grill is a one of a kind South Brevard dining experience offering fresh local seafood and more. Located at the Sebastian Inlet Marina, it’s a great place to relax while enjoying a wide open view of the Indian River Lagoon and check out the BIG Boats coming and going. Arrive by boat or by car, enjoy
air-conditioned indoor seating or the outdoor area.
Pets are welcome in our outdoor dining areas.  Boat parking is available so please come dock and dine. Anywhere on north or south side of docks of The Sebastian Inlet Marina is available to restaurant guests. Please call the marina on vhf 16, a dockhand will assist you with docking.
Yes, we serve on disposable dinnerware and here’s why ... Because we are closely situated to the Indian River Lagoon, every effort is made to limit the number of harsh chemicals used by commercial dishwashing machines. We cannot risk inadvertently polluting the lagoon, we sincerely hope our guests understand this decision.
Special Requests?
Questions about an upcoming event? Wondering what's on the specials board this week?
Drop us a line, and we'll get back to you soon or follow us on social media!
Special Events and Catering
Our restaurant is available for private events: business lunches, dinners, cocktail receptions, and more. We'd love to discuss how to be a part of your next event.
Seasonal and Local
We refuse to compromise on quality in our restaurant. That's why we source fresh, local ingredients.
